Package com.android.extendedWidgets.lists

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionsListItem
    Element list of available Bluetooth or Wifi connections.
    ExplorerApplicationItem
    A list item downloaded applications on the server, which is connected to the application.
    ExplorerApplicationList
    Adapter for list of elements defined in ExplorerApplicationItem.
    ListOfConections
    Adapter for list of elements defined in ConnectionsListItem.
    ListOfVideo
    Adapter for list of elements defined in VideoListItem.
    PreferencesDialogItem
    Element to display a list of possible options in the dialog box that opens when you call a menu with additional options for the item.
    PreferencesDialogItem.ICON
    List of id for PreferencesDialogItem icons for elements.
    PreferencesDialogItem.ID
    List of id for PreferencesDialogItem elements.
    PreferencesDialogItem.NAME
    List of id for PreferencesDialogItem element names.
    PreferencesDialogList
    Adapter for list of elements defined in PreferencesDialogItem.
    VideoListItem
    A list item for help activities that contains list of video tutorials.
    VideoListItem.VIDEO_MINIATURE
    Helper class that contains IDs for video miniatures.
